<br>
I support limitations on guns. I feel that if someone wants to own one, it should be possible. Removal of guns not only punishes the criminals, but it punishes decent citizens as well. This is not the solution.<br>
<br>
What needs to be understood here is that it doesn't matter what laws you create. It doesn't matter what you condemn on a public stage. We're dealing with ppl that are breaking the laws of the land and of humanity.<br>
<br>
I believe many of our problems can be traced back fo family. At the risk of drawing flames, I dare say the women's equality movement contributed to this in an important way. Children require a lot of attention and care. When a member of the family is spending much of their time providing those things, chances are it will have a positive impact on the children's developement and future contributions to society.<br>
<br>
Society has changed. We need to promote ways to deal with these changes to prevent many of the problems we see with youth and younger adults.<br>
<br>
Working parents and single parent families don't cut it. Yes, a child can turn out to be a great person if they have a single parent or both parents working. It's possible. But a child is less likely to do just that.<br>
<br>
Our society needs to have more promotion of a good family structure. Children and young adults need Multiple sources in their life that provide love and guidance. They can't be left to find it on their own. This is the way to disaster.<br>
<br>
The USA has been experiencing a breakdown of the family unit. I come from a completely dysfunctional home. Most of the people i've known had a family riddled with serious problems. I find it hard to recall many friends with a decent home and family setting. This is hurting, not helping.<br>
<br>
We need to place more importance on having a solid, caring family. A group of people that stick together and guide each other through life.<br>
<br>
At the moment USA society and culture places too much importance in the wrong things. This needs to change. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#FFFFFF>- </font><a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter>Vazaelle.com Community Center</a><font color=#FFFFFF> - </font><a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30>The Real World</a> <font color=#FFFFFF> - </font><a href="http://www.vazaelle.com">Vazaelle.com</a><font color=#FFFFFF> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard</a> Ver. 7.246j<br>Copyright 1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

